name: InspireMe
0:
”Alexa open inspire me and tell me something inspiring”
”quote of the day”
”inspire me now”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: inspire me
des:
Everyone needs inspiration in life to do wonders. Begin your morning by hearing motivational words from Alexa using my skill "Inspire Me". 
Enable this skill and then, Invoke by saying "quote of the day" or "inspire me". 
Be inspired, ignited, and motivated!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
